=== Aachen dialect ===
Aachen is at the western end of the [[Benrath line]] that divides [[High German languages|High German]] to the south from the rest of the [[West Germanic languages|West Germanic]] speech area to the north.<ref>{{harvnb|Anon|2013}}.</ref> Aachen's local dialect is called {{lang|de|[[Aachen dialect|Öcher Platt]]}} and belongs to the [[Ripuarian language]].

